        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.SemDist"
      },
      "sc:description": "This package implements methods to calculate information accretion for a given version of the gene ontology and uses this data to calculate remaining uncertainty, misinformation, and semantic similarity for given sets of predicted annotations and true annotations from a protein function predictor.",
